              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "D4PI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ".The neutron were detected by the Polycube 4-pi",
                "thermalization counter, consisting of 12 cylindrical",
                "proportional counters filled with He-3 at the pressure",
