          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*By authors*.The new determination cross section value",
                "turns out to be about 10% smaller than that given in",
                "previous letter(See reference-J,PL/B,664,157,2008),",
                "while the effect of the sources of systematic",
                "uncertainties has proved to be negligible.",
                "*By authors*.In the present neutron-inclusive",
                "measurement, the background contribution has been",
                "carefully identified and evaluated. Since different",
                "sources of systematical uncertainties and of background",
                "are involved, the present data strongly confirm and",
                "support the complementary B-11 inclusive data.",
                "See Rel-Ref."
              ]
            }
